These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-5-1::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, tram
House: craftsman, townhouse
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, satire
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, goat
1. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5
2. the person watching satire movies is the owner of the goat##1
3. the townhouse house is on the right of the craftsman house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Transport          | tram    | motorbike |
| House         | craftsman | townhouse |
| Movie-Genre   | musical    | satire    |
| Pet   | goldfish  | goat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-5-2::.
There 2 different types of food: pomegranate, zucchini
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, lemonade
2 different games are played: backgammon, canasta
There are 2 different nationalities: german, argentine
1. the argentine is somewhere to the right of the person eating pomegranate##5
2. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person playing canasta##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Food          | pomegranate | zucchini   |
| Beverage   | lemonade        | sprite     |
| Game           | backgammon         | canasta     |
| Nationality     | german         | argentine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-5-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, puzzles
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, baccarat
There are 2 different favourite colors: black, emerald
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, mystery
1. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
2. the fonseca-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who likes black##5
3. the baccarat-smoker is the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Hobby         | puzzles      | chess    |
| Cigar           | fonseca | baccarat |
| Color   | emerald       | black    |
| Movie-Genre     | epic    | mystery     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-5-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, canadian
There are 2 different favourite colors: green, brown
2 different games are played: monopoly, backgammon
1. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person playing backgammon##5
2. the dutch is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person who likes green##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Beverage      | coffee  | 7up        |
| Nationality         | canadian | dutch |
| Color   | green    | brown    |
| Game     | backgammon | monopoly        |

