The people have 2 different jobs:  firefighter, scientist
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, january
2 different pets are kept: pony, ferret
1. the firefighter is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
2. the owner of the ferret is in an odd position##4
3. the scientist is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |
| City          | san-francisco | boston      |
| Job           | scientist | firefighter |
| Birthday   | october  | january   |
| Pet         | ferret   | pony     |

